preference.name: ItemRevision_PseudoFolder
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of properties that can be displayed as a pseudo-folder under a node for Item Revision object. All the configured runtime properties defined on the Item Revision business object will be automatically added as preference values during login. If the preference value which is configured as a runtime property is deleted, it will be added back during login. For example, if the preference value "geometric_interfaces" (configured runtime property) defined on the "ItemRevision_PseudoFolder" preference is deleted, it will be added back during login.
